0:{"buildId":"7h74Y9z83_3h3-U7doOR4","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"x:mx-auto x:flex x:max-w-(--nextra-content-width)","children":["$","$L2",null,{"value":[{"value":"Font family","id":"font-family","depth":2},{"value":"Font size (시맨틱)","id":"font-size-시맨틱","depth":2},{"value":"Font weight","id":"font-weight","depth":2},{"value":"Line height","id":"line-height","depth":2}],"children":[["$","$L3",null,{}],["$","$L4",null,{"metadata":{"title":"Typography","filePath":"content/foundation/typography.mdx"},"sourceCode":"# Typography\n\n타이포그래피 토큰은 **시맨틱 이름**으로 정의되며, 테마별로 실제 폰트/크기 값이 매핑됩니다.\n\n## Font family\n\n| 토큰   | 용도           | basic 예시     | game 예시   | crayon 예시   |\n| ------ | -------------- | ------------- | ----------- | ------------- |\n| sans   | 본문, UI       | Inter         | DungGeunMo  | 온글잎-승훈체 |\n| mono   | 코드          | Roboto Mono   | 동일        | 동일          |\n| crayon | (crayon 전용)  | —             | —           | 온글잎-승훈체 |\n\n## Font size (시맨틱)\n\n- **xsmall**, **small**, **medium**, **large**, **xlarge** — 본문·UI 크기\n- **display-small**, **display-medium**, **display-large** — 큰 제목용\n\n## Font weight\n\n- **regular** (400)\n- **medium** (500)\n- **semibold** (600)\n- **bold** (700)\n\n## Line height\n\n각 font size에 대응하는 line height 토큰이 있으며, 테마에서 함께 지정됩니다.\n\n`Text` 컴포넌트의 `size`, `weight` prop이 이 토큰과 연결됩니다.","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"nextra-skip-nav"}],["$","main",null,{"data-pagefind-body":true,"children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-bold x:mt-2 x:text-4xl","children":["Typography","$undefined"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":["타이포그래피 토큰은 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"시맨틱 이름"}],"으로 정의되며, 테마별로 실제 폰트/크기 값이 매핑됩니다."]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"font-family","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-10 x:border-b x:pb-1 x:text-3xl nextra-border","children":["Font family",["$","$L5",null,{"id":"font-family"}]]}],"\n",["$","table",null,{"className":"x:block x:overflow-x-auto nextra-scrollbar x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:p-0","children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"토큰","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"용도","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"basic 예시","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"game 예시","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"crayon 예시","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}]],"className":"x:m-0 x:border-t x:border-gray-300 x:p-0 x:dark:border-gray-600 x:even:bg-gray-100 x:even:dark:bg-gray-600/20"}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"sans","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"본문, UI","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Inter","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"DungGeunMo","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"온글잎-승훈체","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}]],"className":"x:m-0 x:border-t x:border-gray-300 x:p-0 x:dark:border-gray-600 x:even:bg-gray-100 x:even:dark:bg-gray-600/20"}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"mono","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x